page.title: 17MY DAY, EAST BARKWITH
page.content: {8.30am}After breakfast I brush my teeth, then I put my flask and box in my bag and set off for school. After crossing through the churchyard and going down the road I come to the school. After a quick game of Dodge- ball we go inside. {9.00am}School starts. After Assembly, which consists of a hymn,three prayers and the Lord's Prayer, we have maths, then a playtime, then English. {12.00 noon} We have dinner, followed by a playtime, followed by a topic. After that there is a playtime, and then it is P.E. or music,then it is time to go home. {3.30pm} I go home and watch television for a while, then I have my tea. After that I watch television, and go to bed about {8.30pm} I am eleven years old.
